snippet.title: Monument Valley Game Release Trailer by ustwo
snippet.description:
Have you played the smash hit mobile game 'Monument Valley' or 'Assemble with Care' ? let us know in the comments below. We are ustwo (part of the Fampany Creative Group)

Founded by two best friends, “Mills” & “Sinx” in London in 2004, we set out to create a “Fampany”, marrying the best of family and company.

contact me  @millsustwo  
https://linktr.ee/millsustwo
https://www.ustwo.com

We believe that by caring deeply for our people, clients, and partners, we can unleash our “collective genius”. That means mastering the art of collaboration, crafting the optimal conditions for a team to perform at its absolute best, in an environment of diverse backgrounds, thoughts, views, opinions and life experiences. 


Music by the brilliant OBFUSC: http://www.obfusc.net/
